title: 02/10/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 02/10/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, we're joined by guests from across the world's landscape. NBC's Peter King joins us to discuss Russell Wilson's comments and who he voted for in the Super Bowl MVP voting. Tim Cowlishaw from the Dallas Morning News shares why he thinks Dak Prescott was left out of the Cowboys hype video. Dr. Mark Adickes answers what exactly is turf toe. And 76ers Head Coach Doc Rivers explains why he doesn't go by Doc in Philadelphia.
